85
00:05:50,039 --> 00:05:54,925
Poems are written that resonate still and a river runs through it.

86
00:05:56,085 --> 00:06:07,168
Our valley is a place of revolution, where new voices seek a new solution that doesn't begin with a cash contribution, that doesn't end with filth and pollution.

87
00:06:07,728 --> 00:06:20,992
Voices that hush when justice calls and push when progress slowly calls, presenting new and clear demands with concrete 10-year master plans and a river runs through it.

88
00:06:22,086 --> 00:06:47,344
Our valley is a place of revelation where cooperative efforts rebuild and the local folk join the highly skilled to reclaim, rebrand, and re-engineer with the local folk who volunteer to pluck the refuge from marsh and shore with only the thought to refresh and restore so future folks embrace and explore and the river runs through it.

89
00:06:48,347 --> 00:07:07,597
Our valley is a place of vibrancy that takes great pride in its energy, that seeks out moments of synergy, that wraps its models in honesty, that guards its resources zealously, that seeks its level with urgency, and a river runs through it.

90
00:07:08,830 --> 00:07:27,745
Our valley is a place of true rebirth, as we try to protect our precious earth, where good people meet to set things right, and the cleanup ensues through the waning light, and then the party takes over the night, and the food and the music is out of sight.

91
00:07:28,365 --> 00:07:37,292
We gather our kin at the father's shore, and labor together to open the door, and a river runs through it.

